      "metadata_json": "{\"branch\":\"main\",\"confidence\":95,\"prompt\":\"Implement the following plan:\\n\\n# Production Readiness Review â€” ATProtoPDS (Small Self-Hoster)\\n\\n## Context\\n\\nProduction readiness assessment and remediation plan for self-hosting the Objective-C ATProtoPDS implementation. The codebase is substantially complete (96/96 core AT Protocol methods, OAuth/DPoP, SQLite persistence, logging) but has several gaps. Scope: **single-machine small self-hoster**, not distributed deployment.\\n\\n[Full plan omitted for brevity â€” see conversation transcript]\\n\\nFixes implemented:\\nC1: Wire Resend email provider into PDSApplication.m\\nC2: Enforce JWT issuer at startup (exit(1) if production + pds.local)\\nC3: Reverse proxy / HTTPS deployment documentation\\nH1: Content-Type header (was already present)\\nH2: Parse Resend error JSON body (name/message fields)\\nH3: Persist token invalidation to file (survives restarts)\\nH4: Warn on plain-text admin password at startup\\nH5: Warn on X-Admin-Token in production at startup\\nM1: Add 409 to retryable HTTP status codes\\nM2: Register NSUncaughtExceptionHandler (C function, not block)\\nM3: Apply WAL + performance PRAGMAs to service DB pools\"}"
    },
